			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-547712">
									

<p>Brings up a interesting topic: What do you do outside of work? Some folks probably never leave the base, but some must. Most of the folks allowed out probably know next to nothing, but what about folks like researchers and MTF members who are allowed out? How do you just go back to the world?</p>
<p>I have to imagine it's like soldiers just coming back from a war zone. You remember life, and how things used to be, but…you've changed. All in all, good work so far, and i'm looking forward to reading more.</p>

